---
import { categories } from '@/data/categories';
---

<footer class="mt-16 border-t border-stone-100 py-10">
  <div class="content-width">
    <nav class="mb-6" aria-label="카테고리 링크">
      <ul class="flex flex-wrap gap-x-4 gap-y-1.5">
        {categories.map((cat) => (
          <li>
            <a
              href={cat.path}
              class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-sub)] no-underline transition-colors duration-150 hover:text-[var(--color-text)]"
            >
              {cat.name}
            </a>
          </li>
        ))}
      </ul>
    </nav>

    <div class="mt-8 border-t border-stone-100 pt-6 text-xs leading-relaxed text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">
      <p>
        이 포스팅은 쿠팡 파트너스 활동의 일환으로, 이에 따른 일정액의 수수료를 제공받습니다.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-2">&copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} 휙 hwick.shop</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
